      "writtenOn": "2020-08-25T02:06:26Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "For exported APIs (i.e. ResolveHostFromFiles), I recommend NOT supporting tildes.\n\nThere\u0027s no necessity to support tildes in arguments of ResolveHostFromFiles (in contrast to \"include\" in config files where supporting tildes are necessary from config spec). Of course, it is possible that users of this package may really want to expand tildes, but if there\u0027s such need, we can just export expandLeadingTilde.\n\nIn general, please avoid coupling two unrelated things in a function --- in this case, expanding tildes and parsing config files.",
