      "writtenOn": "2020-08-26T20:23:27Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I have changed the structure unit tests and reduced almost 600 lines. All tests used one single set of the config files except for two test cases. I didn\u0027t use the structure that you suggested. I used a common test function instead. It is easy for me to read. Also, I also add comments to the test configuration to indicate what each rule is trying to test. I hope it is ok. Please review.",
